  "1836560": {
    "name": "以太与铁",
    "steam_appid": 1836560,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/75fa6d5379d943446e86ca69862f4498.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1560 height=224 /></span><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/fea92fc8f5d73dd18b1a3d17355c869a.poster.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/fea92fc8f5d73dd18b1a3d17355c869a.webm?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/fea92fc8f5d73dd18b1a3d17355c869a.mp4?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纽约街头危机四伏，孤军奋战注定举步维艰。你需要招募一群各具特色、能力非凡的伙伴，深入体验他们的故事，并肩作战。每位成员都有独特的专长与技能，在关键时刻往往能成为决定胜负的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/72cfc07cce82d18352adb5faa047cf7e.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1560 height=224 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong> </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/138d898885d7183b1866e9c26e8d0e72.poster.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/138d898885d7183b1866e9c26e8d0e72.webm?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/138d898885d7183b1866e9c26e8d0e72.mp4?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对走私犯而言，一辆顶级座驾既是生存之道，也是身份象征。游戏提供多种炫酷的以太动力载具，并在传统回合制战斗的基础上，创新加入基于载具的策略玩法，带来耳目一新的战斗体验。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可自由打造专属座驾，随心所欲地进行改装：或许你偏爱轻盈敏捷、迅速脱离险境的速度型座驾？也可能你更青睐厚实稳重、火力十足的重装型战车？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong></strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/aed9c35bf1269aaaf2c0b6c42cc7669f.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1560 height=224 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/66119d4f3bb3d068d836abb76aacafea.poster.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/66119d4f3bb3d068d836abb76aacafea.webm?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/66119d4f3bb3d068d836abb76aacafea.mp4?t=1771544553\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作由曾参与创作《孤岛惊魂》、《质量效应》和《主权辛迪加》等经典作品的资深编剧团队倾力打造，呈现了一个以反重力以太技术改写历史的新世界。科技飞跃带来了壮丽的浮空城市景观，但也加剧了社会阶层的割裂与矛盾。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏世界观经过精心考据，深受真实1930年代纽约的启发。你将穿梭于城市的阴暗小巷和罪恶角落，欣赏充满时代气息的华丽建筑，层层揭开这座城市背后权谋与贪婪交织的真相。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的每个抉择都至关重要，不仅决定自身命运，更将改变整座城市的未来：你会成为众人仰望的救世主、远离纷争的叛逆隐士，抑或是在权力纷争与高风险博弈中淬炼成反抗暴政的传奇人物？  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1836560/extras/979b14482cce222c99635ff5af856cf8.avif?t=1771544553\" width=1560 height=224 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>深入地下世界：</strong>摸索隐秘通道，躲避敌人追踪，巧妙隐藏违禁货物，始终保持领先，逃脱各路势力的追击与围堵。或许，你还会在险境中邂逅反抗组织，并肩战斗。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你的选择决定一切：</strong>你的每个决定都会深刻影响纽约城的命运与市民的未来，最终决定他们能否在这个充斥着操控与暴力的腐败世界中重获希望。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>培养你的专长：</strong>提升你的狡诈、智慧和胆魄三大属性，在战斗与社交场景中提升成功几率。不过请记住，无论你多么精明强悍，命运的骰子总会带来意想不到的惊喜或灾祸。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>潇洒驾驶，随你所愿：</strong>自由改装强化你的以太动力座驾，用走私者特有的各种装备——隐秘隔间、烟幕释放器，甚至喷火器，打造最适合你的走私风格。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精致独特的视觉风格：</strong>游戏整体美术风格深受1930年代经典侦探漫画和装饰艺术风潮影响，呈现出独特、迷人的视觉体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>全程语音演绎：</strong>亲耳聆听纽约城居民的声音与故事，以最直观的方式感受这段架空历史。他们的故事或诙谐幽默，或哲思隽永，却往往逃不过命运的悲剧色彩。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 法语, 德语, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 俄语, 简体中文, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 波兰语<br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
